<exercise number="11"><statement><p>The population of Summerville is currently 12 hundred people.<ol marker="a">
    <li><p>Write a formula for the population if it grows at a constant rate of 1.5 hundred people per year. What is the population after 3 years?</p></li>
    <li><p>Write a formula for the population if it has a constant growth factor of 1.5 per year. What is the population after 3 years?   </p></li></ol>
